        <Parent_String>Nubian (culture or style) [300015709], ancient East African [300015702], Ancient African [300015690], African (general, continental cultures) [300015647], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
